def ATR(df, n):  
    i = 0  
    TR_l = [0]  
    while i < df.index[-1]:  
        TR = max(df.get_value(i + 1, 'high'), df.get_value(i, 'close')) - min(df.get_value(i + 1, 'low'), df.get_value(i, 'close'))  
        TR_l.append(TR)  
        i = i + 1  
    TR_s = pd.Series(TR_l)  
    ATR = pd.Series(pd.ewma(TR_s, span = n, min_periods = n), name = 'atr')  
    df = df.join(ATR)
    return df

trade_long=1
trade_short=1
long_pos = 0
short_pos = 0
total_pl=0
N_days=len(NIFTY50)-2
trade_dict = {}
open_multiplier=1.15
close_multiplier=2.75
short_open_multiplier=1.15
short_close_multiplier=2.75

for X in tqdm(NIFTY50.index):
    #if X < N_days and (NIFTY50.at[X,'date']+BDay()).strftime('%a')=="Wed":
    if X < N_days:
        # previous day stretch
        stretch_10sma=NIFTY50.at[X,'stretch_10sma']
        # NIFTY open
        n50open=NIFTY50.at[X+1,'open']
        # NIFTY high
        n50high=NIFTY50.at[X+1,'high']
        # NIFTY low
        n50low=NIFTY50.at[X+1,'low']
        # NIFTY close
        n50close=NIFTY50.at[X+1,'close']
        # NIFTY next day open
        n50new_open=NIFTY50.at[X+1,'open']
        longentry,longstop,longtarget = n50new_open+stretch_10sma*open_multiplier,n50new_open-stretch_10sma*0.2,n50new_open+stretch_10sma*close_multiplier
        shortentry,shortstop,shorttarget = n50new_open-stretch_10sma*short_open_multiplier,n50new_open+stretch_10sma*0.2,n50new_open-stretch_10sma*short_close_multiplier
        #longentry,longstop,longtarget = n50new_open+stretch_10sma*open_multiplier,n50new_open,n50new_open+stretch_10sma*close_multiplier
        #shortentry,shortstop,shorttarget = n50new_open-stretch_10sma*short_open_multiplier,n50new_open,n50new_open-stretch_10sma*short_close_multiplier
        # run minute loop from tradeday (day+1)
        tradeday=NIFTY50.at[X+1,'date']
        # look for data between tradeday and tradeday+1 days
        dayafter=NIFTY50.at[X+2,'date']
        #print tradeday, dayafter, stretch_10sma
        pl=0
        tick=0
        day_order=0
        order_completed=0
        for ti,op,hi,lo,cl in N50MINUTE.query('date_time >= @tradeday and date_time <= @dayafter').itertuples(index=False):
            tick=tick+1
            # if first bar
            # set entry,stop,profit target for the day based on first 1 min bar today
            # and previous days stretch_10sma
            #if ti.strftime('%H:%M:%S') == "10:00:00":
            #    longentry,longstop,longtarget = op+stretch_10sma*open_multiplier,op,op+stretch_10sma*close_multiplier
            #    shortentry,shortstop,shorttarget = op-stretch_10sma*open_multiplier,op,op-stretch_10sma*close_multiplier
            if ti.strftime('%H:%M:%S') > "09:16:00" and ti.strftime('%H:%M:%S') < "14:59:00":
                if cl > longentry and trade_long == 1 and long_pos == 0 and day_order < 1 :
                    # enter long
                    day_order = day_order+1
                    long_pos = 1
                    o_time=tick
                    o_type="Long"
                    o_price=longentry
                if cl < shortentry and trade_short == 1 and short_pos == 0 and day_order < 1 :
                    # enter short
                    day_order = day_order+1
                    short_pos = 1
                    o_time=tick
                    o_type="Short"
                    o_price=shortentry    
            if ti.strftime('%H:%M:%S') > "09:16:00" and ti.strftime('%H:%M:%S') < "14:59:00":
                if hi > longtarget and day_order >= 1 and trade_long == 1 and long_pos == 1:
                    long_pos = 0
                    c_time=tick
                    c_price=longtarget
                    win_loss="Win"
                    c_type = "Profit"
                    pl=c_price-o_price
                    # close long at profit
                    order_completed=1
                if lo < longstop and day_order >= 1 and trade_long == 1 and long_pos == 1:
                    long_pos = 0
                    c_time=tick
                    c_price=longstop
                    win_loss="Loss"
                    c_type = "Stop"
                    pl=c_price-o_price
                    # close long as stop loss hit
                    order_completed=1
                if lo < shorttarget and day_order >= 1 and trade_short == 1 and short_pos == 1:
                    short_pos = 0
                    c_time=tick
                    c_price=shorttarget
                    win_loss="Win"
                    c_type = "Profit"
                    pl=o_price-c_price
                    # close short at profit
                    order_completed=1
                if hi > shortstop and day_order >= 1 and trade_short == 1 and short_pos == 1:
                    short_pos = 0
                    c_time=tick
                    c_price=shortstop
                    win_loss="Loss"
                    c_type = "Stop"
                    pl=o_price-c_price
                    # close short as stop loss hit
                    order_completed=1
            # if last bar, then close open posistions
            if ti.strftime('%H:%M:%S') == "15:00:00":
                if long_pos == 1:
                    long_pos = 0
                    c_time=tick
                    c_price=op
                    win_loss="Win"
                    c_type = "EOD"
                    pl=c_price-o_price
                    order_completed=1
                if short_pos == 1:
                    short_pos = 0
                    c_time=tick
                    c_price=op
                    win_loss="Win"
                    c_type = "EOD"
                    pl=o_price-c_price
                    order_completed=1
            if order_completed == 1 and long_pos == 0 and short_pos == 0:
                #day_order=0
                order_completed=0
                total_pl=total_pl+pl
                #'o_time': o_time.strftime('%H:%M:%S'),
                trade_dict.update({len (trade_dict)+1: {'date': tradeday,
                                                        'stretch_10sma': stretch_10sma,
                                                        'n50open': n50open,
                                                        'n50high': n50high,
                                                        'n50low': n50low,
                                                        'n50close': n50close,
                                                        's_l': o_type,
                                                        'o_time': o_time,
                                                        'o_price': o_price,
                                                        'c_time': c_time,
                                                        'c_price': c_price,
                                                        'c_type': c_type,
                                                        'pl': pl,
                                                        'total_pl': total_pl,
                                                        'win_loss': win_loss}})
# finished loop now calculate results 
trade=pd.DataFrame.from_dict(trade_dict).T
trade = trade[['date','stretch_10sma','n50open','n50high','n50low','n50close','s_l','o_time','o_price','c_time','c_price','c_type','pl','total_pl','win_loss']]
win_pct=(trade.query('win_loss == "Win"')[['pl']].count()/trade[['pl']].count()*100).values[0]
total_pl=trade[['pl']].sum().values[0]
total_trades=len(trade)
profit_factor=(trade.query('win_loss == "Win"')[['pl']].sum() / trade.query('win_loss == "Loss"')[['pl']].sum()).abs().values[0]
avg_win=trade.query('win_loss == "Win"')[['pl']].apply(lambda row: np.mean(row),axis=0).values[0]
avg_loss=trade.query('win_loss == "Loss"')[['pl']].apply(lambda row: np.mean(row),axis=0).values[0]
n_wins=trade.query('win_loss == "Win"')[['pl']].count().values[0]
n_loss=trade.query('win_loss == "Loss"')[['pl']].count().values[0]
trade['day_of_week'] = trade['date'].dt.weekday_name

print "Win %        :", win_pct
print "Total Profit :", total_pl

%%time
result_dict = {}
#print "Run Number,open_multiplier,close_multiplier\n", 
for open_multiplier in tqdm(np.arange(0.85, 1.26, 0.01)):
    for close_multiplier in np.arange(2, 3.55, 0.05):
        #print run_num,",", round(open_multiplier,2),",", round(close_multiplier,2)
        win_pct,total_pl,total_trades,profit_factor,avg_win,avg_loss,open_multiplier_r,close_multiplier_r=Open_S(NIFTY50, N50MINUTE, open_multiplier, close_multiplier)
        result_dict.update({len (result_dict)+1: {'win_pct': win_pct,
                                        'total_pl': total_pl,
                                        'total_trades': total_trades,
                                        'profit_factor': profit_factor,
                                        'avg_win': avg_win,
                                        'avg_loss': avg_loss,
                                        'open_multiplier': open_multiplier_r,
                                        'close_multiplier': close_multiplier_r}})
result=pd.DataFrame.from_dict(result_dict).T
result=result[['win_pct','profit_factor','total_pl','total_trades','avg_win','avg_loss','open_multiplier','close_multiplier']]

trade_long=1
trade_short=1
long_pos = 0
short_pos = 0
total_pl=0
N_days=len(NIFTY50)-2
trade_dict = {}
open_multiplier=1.15
close_multiplier=3
short_open_multiplier=1.15
short_close_multiplier=3

for index,date,op,hi,lo,cl,ol,oh,oc,hl,daily_stretch,stretch_10sma in tqdm(NIFTY50[['date','open','high','low','close','ol','oh','oc','hl','daily_stretch','stretch_10sma']].itertuples(index=True)):
    if index>1 and NIFTY50.at[index-1,'close'] > NIFTY50.at[index-1,'hl15sma']:
        total_pl=total_pl+cl-op
        win_loss="Win"
        if cl-op < 0:
            win_loss="Loss"
        trade_dict.update({len (trade_dict)+1: {'date': date,
                                                'stretch_10sma': stretch_10sma,
                                                'n50open': op,
                                                'n50high': hi,
                                                'n50low': lo,
                                                'n50close': cl,
                                                's_l': "Long",
                                                'o_time': "Open",
                                                'o_price': op,
                                                'c_time': "Close",
                                                'c_price': cl,
                                                'c_type': "EOD",
                                                'pl': cl-op,
                                                'total_pl': total_pl,
                                                'win_loss': win_loss}})

    if index>1 and NIFTY50.at[index-1,'close'] < NIFTY50.at[index-1,'hl15sma']:
        total_pl=total_pl+op-cl
        win_loss="Win"
        if op-cl < 0:
            win_loss="Loss"
        trade_dict.update({len (trade_dict)+1: {'date': date,
                                                'stretch_10sma': stretch_10sma,
                                                'n50open': op,
                                                'n50high': hi,
                                                'n50low': lo,
                                                'n50close': cl,
                                                's_l': "Short",
                                                'o_time': "Open",
                                                'o_price': op,
                                                'c_time': "Close",
                                                'c_price': cl,
                                                'c_type': "EOD",
                                                'pl': op-cl,
                                                'total_pl': total_pl,
                                                'win_loss': win_loss}})
# finished loop now calculate results 
trade=pd.DataFrame.from_dict(trade_dict).T
trade = trade[['date','stretch_10sma','n50open','n50high','n50low','n50close','s_l','o_time','o_price','c_time','c_price','c_type','pl','total_pl','win_loss']]
win_pct=(trade.query('win_loss == "Win"')[['pl']].count()/trade[['pl']].count()*100).values[0]
total_pl=trade[['pl']].sum().values[0]
total_trades=len(trade)
profit_factor=(trade.query('win_loss == "Win"')[['pl']].sum() / trade.query('win_loss == "Loss"')[['pl']].sum()).abs().values[0]
avg_win=trade.query('win_loss == "Win"')[['pl']].apply(lambda row: np.mean(row),axis=0).values[0]
avg_loss=trade.query('win_loss == "Loss"')[['pl']].apply(lambda row: np.mean(row),axis=0).values[0]
n_wins=trade.query('win_loss == "Win"')[['pl']].count().values[0]
n_loss=trade.query('win_loss == "Loss"')[['pl']].count().values[0]
trade['day_of_week'] = trade['date'].dt.weekday_name

print "Win %        :", win_pct
print "Total Profit :", total_pl
print "Total Trades :", total_trades
print "Profit Factor:", profit_factor
print "Avg Win      :", avg_win
print "Avg Loss     :", avg_loss
print "Wins: Loss   = ",n_wins,":",n_loss
